Carpe Diem - A Latin phrase for "seize the day." In other words, enjoy the present and don't worry about the future. I'm still trying to see how the title relates to the game...

If you want to go on a quick feels trip (in 2-7 mins, depending how fast you read), play this free game. I'm not much into visual novels (I don't have the attention span for them), but this one is not bad. If it puts things into perspective, I thought Sakura Spirit was kinda boring. Katawa Shoujo (also free) is probably my favorite, but I didn't finish it.

Also, the achievement spoils the game. D'oh! This is probably the only game I'll ever perfect (earning all of the achievements), ;_;
